<br>
I've been pondering giving FV a try for a while now. So far everything I've wondered at has not been an actual problem. My question a bit ago concerning the TLC effect on Trade Skills, for example.<br>
<br>
But there is another curiosity. I was wondering if trolls and iksars would be able to group together or cast on each other. Both evil, but both serving different deities...I think. Bertox and Inny? Anyone have an idea of the chances there? Haven't had much luck finding out any information on the web.<br>
<br>
Thanks in advance,<br>
Eredhel <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ueredhel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eredhel</A> at: 1/22/02 6:48:31 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umaladominus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maladominus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/22/02 7:03:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1163.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Religious compatibility of trolls and iksars.</span><hr size=1> Cazic Thule is the Creator of both the Trolls and the Iksars.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <br>
<br>
Both races are evil-aligned. <br>
<br>
Both races regenerate. <br>
<br>
Both races can EASILY group together in FV server, other role playing considerations aside. <br>
<br>
In this server, you *will* run into a couple of Iksar-only role playing guilds who preach Iksar racial superiority and xenophobia..... I doubt those Iksars will even admit to the fact that the Trolls are a kindred race, since they all share the same creator. <br>
<br>
You can group together based on aligments. Trolls and Iksars are generally evil aligned in Firiona Vie.<br>
<br>
BTW...... many Trolls do worship Innoruuk.... but Trolls have a choice at game start to worship either Cazic or Innoruuk. It never made sense to me why the majority of Trolls simply dont choose to worship their original creator, Cazic-Thule. <br>
<br>
EDIT -- ok I found out why most Trolls are encouraged to worship Innoruuk instead of Cazic-Thule. In the Verant EQ histories.... it mentions something about Trolls being Cazic's original &quot;children&quot;, and then in a later age, he forsaked them as his favored race.... which then led Cazic to create a newer more intelligent and more robust race, the Iksar then became his favorite children, his chosen people.<br>
<br>
